snippet.title: Leo Steel - Sick Old Game (With original music)
snippet.description:
A great little shockwave game

Play here
http://www.freearcade.com/LeoSteel.shock/LeoSteel.html

To play you need to be using Internet explorer, firefox or safari and have shockwave player installed on your computer.

Download shockwave player 
http://get.adobe.com/shockwave/otherversions/
